Love song for you！｣

134
00:11:35,312 --> 00:11:40,668
｢ｲｴｲ ｲｴｲ ｲｴｲ ｲｴｲ｣

135
00:11:40,668 --> 00:11:46,868
｢Love song for you！｣

136
00:11:49,309 --> 00:11:52,479
